<h2>Welcome</h2>
<p>Upcoming events: April 09, May 14 &amp; June 11. <a href="mailto:emom.sydney@gmail.com">Send us an email</a> if you'd like to play, otherwise <a href="https://events.humanitix.com/sydney-electronic-music-open-mic-night/tickets"  target="_blank" rel="noopener">get your tickets here!</a></p>
<hr>
<p>The Sydney Electronic Music Open Mic (EMOM) is a monthly event showcasing local electronic music talent in an open mic format. Whether you're a seasoned performer or just starting out, EMOM provides a supportive platform to share your music with an enthusiastic audience.</p>
